<p>Our choice to abstract app code into JSON presented many chanllenges, the first was </p>

<p><code>how do we perform actions with just JSON?</code></p>

<p>Our solution was to create a new class.
This &quot;action&quot; class would allow us to define actions as JSON objects.</p>
